# Assets Investment Placements Loans And Debt Securities Amount

## identifier
de2043

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, for the net market value of investments that include (but are not limited to):
- Interest-rate related investments, loans and advances of the entity;
- Placements, loans with, and debt securities issued by Individuals, Unlisted private incorporated entities, and Unlisted private unincorporated entities (including unlisted private trusts);
- Other placements, loans and debt securities;
- Short term debt securities (e.g. bills of exchange, certificates of deposit, commercial paper, promissory notes); and
- Long term debt securities (e.g. Treasury Bonds, securitised instruments).
This should exclude:
- interest-rate related cash; and
- interest rate related derivative contracts.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.Investment.PlacementsLoansAndDebtSecurities.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo7.02.00
- period=instant
